### **3. 26_LogPatternExplorer**  
**Description:**  
Analyzes log files and finds repeating errors or anomalies over time.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogPatternExplorer - Log Analyzer Tool

LogPatternExplorer highlights recurring issues in large log files by grouping similar lines and showing frequencies.

## Features
- Frequency summary  
- Works on large logs  
- Supports keyword filters  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/26_LogPatternExplorer.git
cd 26_LogPatternExplorer
python analyze.py /var/log/syslog
